metadata.title: (12-pack) Teal Awareness Ribbon Bracelets, Variety Pack - Wholesale Bulk Pack of 12 Silicone Rubber Wristbands to Symbolize Hope, Courage, Strength, and Support - Unisex for Men Women Teens
features: Pack of 12 Teal awareness ribbon bracelets for supporting a variety of Teal ribbon awareness causes, including: Anti Bullying Awareness, PTSD, OCD, Agoraphobia, Panic Disorder and Anxiety Disorder Awareness, Cervical Cancer, Ovarian Cancer Awareness, Sexual Assault Awareness and more.
Includes an assortment of 3 unique designs: Teal Awareness Ribbon Support Band, Change Begins with Awareness, and Teal Awareness Words of Courage, Strength, and Encouragement

Conveniently packaged in bulk, these versatile bracelets make great giveaway items and awareness gifts. Wear them to show support for friends and family members, and to help raise awareness for research and education on behalf of your cause.

Made from comfort-fit silicone rubber, these wrist bands are comfortable enough for daily wear, and will not snag on clothing. This wholesale pack of 1 dozen bracelets includes unisex designs that can be worn by both him and her.
Size: 8 inches around and slightly stretchable; Fits most adult men, women, and teens
description: This wholesale bulk lot of 1 dozen teal awareness wristbands includes an assortment of silicone rubber bracelets for supporting teal awareness ribbon causes, including: Anti-Bullying Awareness, Agoraphobia, Panic Disorder and Anxiety Disorder, Post Traumatic Stress Disorder (PTSD), Obsessive Compulsive Disorder (OCD), Sexual Assault Awareness, Dissociative Disorders, Food Allergies, Ovarian Cancer, Cervical Cancer Awareness and more. Each pack includes 3 different designs to give you a diverse assortment of awareness bands for friends and family members, nurses and patients. Conveniently packaged in bulk, these bracelets make great giveaway gifts, hospital gifts, and fundraising merchandise for Awareness Month. You can easily place these small awareness gifts into goodie bags for your awareness event, or into hospital care packages. Use the wrist bands to increase awareness about research and education issues, prevention and treatment. This variety pack assortment contains several unisex designs that are suitable for him or her.
